des: Jorge Mateo grounds into a double play, shortstop Ernie Clement to second baseman Davis Schneider to first baseman Spencer Horwitz.   Austin Hays to 3rd.    Ramón Urías out at 2nd.    Jorge Mateo out at 1st.
Ramón Urías singles on a line drive to center fielder Nathan Lukes.   Austin Hays to 2nd.
Ryan O'Hearn flies out to left fielder Rafael Lantigua.
Ryan Mountcastle out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Garrett Spain.   Gunnar Henderson scores.
Anthony Santander grounds out, pitcher CJ Van Eyk to second baseman Davis Schneider to first baseman Spencer Horwitz.   Adley Rutschman scores.    Gunnar Henderson to 3rd.
Gunnar Henderson doubles (5) on a line drive to right fielder Garrett Spain.   Adley Rutschman to 3rd.
